trans-unit.source: Acts as the base class for all property entry classes.
trans-unit.target: 作为所有属性项类的基类。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.PropertyEntry> is the base class for all property entry classes; you cannot create an instance of this class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.PropertyEntry> 是所有的属性条目类; 的基类无法创建此类的实例。

trans-unit.source: It defines fields that are used in the derived classes <xref:System.Web.UI.BoundPropertyEntry>, <xref:System.Web.UI.BuilderPropertyEntry>, <xref:System.Web.UI.ComplexPropertyEntry>, <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplatePropertyEntry>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.SimplePropertyEntry>.
trans-unit.target: 它定义在派生类中使用的字段<xref:System.Web.UI.BoundPropertyEntry>， <xref:System.Web.UI.BuilderPropertyEntry>， <xref:System.Web.UI.ComplexPropertyEntry>， <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplatePropertyEntry>，和<xref:System.Web.UI.SimplePropertyEntry>。

trans-unit.source: The page parser uses property entry classes during parsing to represent expressions found within server control tags.
trans-unit.target: 页分析器在分析过程中使用属性项类来表示服务器控件标记内找到的表达式。

trans-unit.source: Gets the type of the class that declares this member.
trans-unit.target: 获取声明此成员的类的类型。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> that declares this member.
Gets or sets the value pertaining to the filter portion of an expression.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置与表达式的筛选器部分有关的值。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> containing the value of the filter on an expression.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.String" />，它包含表达式上的筛选器的值。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the property name that the expression applies to.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置表达式所应用到的属性名称。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> containing the property name.
Gets or sets an object containing attributes of the property the expression applies to.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个对象，该对象包含表达式所应用到的属性的特性。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Reflection.PropertyInfo" /> containing the attributes of the property.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.Reflection.PropertyInfo" />，它包含属性的特性。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the type of the entry.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置属性项的类型。
